    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为新的AI客服系统画一个完整的架构图。核心是一个基于大模型的对话系统，我得先跟你对齐一下整体思路。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "LLM Connect",
        "Agents/Tools",
        "Frontend Web App"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。这个系统最终用户是谁？是普通网民还是内部员工？这会影响我们怎么画外部实体。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Chatbot users"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是面向普通用户的公开聊天机器人。所以最外层应该是一批👥 Chatbot users，他们通过Web界面进来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Chatbot users",
        "Frontend Web App"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把Users放在最左边，用外部实体的样式。然后连到Frontend Web App，标注为\"User Interacts\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Chatbot users",
        "Frontend Web App"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "用户进来之后必须先认证。我们需要一个独立的User Authentication服务，跟Frontend分开画。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User Authentication",
        "Frontend Web App"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：Frontend把认证请求发给Auth，然后Auth返回认证结果给Frontend，双向箭头？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User Authentication",
        "Frontend Web App"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，标注分别是\"User Authenticates\"和\"User Authentication\"。Auth通过之后，Frontend才能把请求往后传。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User Authentication",
        "Frontend Web App"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了。接下来Frontend连到哪里？直接连大模型吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
